Introduction

NXT, also known as tripleS NXT, was the sixth sub-unit of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS.

On October 31, 2023, the reveal of S17, S18, S19, and S20 was teased through the YouTube video "tripleS NEXT". A new teaser, titled "tripleS NXT (?)" was released on December 14. Four days later, on December 18, a scheduler for the unit was posted on the group's official SNS.

On December 21, 2023, Lynn was introduced as S17, the unit's first member. JooBin was introduced as S18 on December 22, followed by HaYeon as S19 on December 23. Finally, ShiOn was introduced as S20, the unit's last member, on December 24.

They debuted on December 23, 2023, with the digital single "Just Do It".
